lead_paragraph: Sven Andrighetto was the only player to score in a five-round shootout, leading the Montreal Canadiens past the Carolina Hurricanes 2-1 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Andrighetto's SO Goal Lifts Canadiens Over Hurricanes 2-1
